00:42:15.908 --> 00:42:17.952
por tu propio bien.

00:42:18.702 --> 00:42:20.704
Haz la vista gorda.

00:42:20.788 --> 00:42:22.081
Cierra esa boca.

00:42:27.670 --> 00:42:28.837
No eres humano.

00:42:30.464 --> 00:42:31.507
